				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BB%81n-%C4%90%E1%BB%97/B%C3%A1-L%C4%83ng-o%C3%A1n-bi%E1%BB%87t/poem-soi5S6J6F_rLg4r525V3tA">Bá Lăng oán biệt - 灞陵怨別</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BB%81n-%C4%90%E1%BB%97/author-qvR5jQ1KJBBzJ7wiP-fcNA">Tiền Đỗ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/B%E1%BA%AFc-chinh-B%E1%BA%AFc-quy-ch%C3%AD-Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-m%E1%BA%B7c-ch%E1%BA%BF-ph%C3%B3ng-v%C3%A3ng-Phu-Ch%C3%A2u-t%C3%A1c/poem-xRXhuUOmluK39LpCU7hkCA">Bắc chinh - Bắc quy chí Phụng Tường, mặc chế phóng vãng Phu Châu tác - 北征－北歸至鳳翔，墨制放往鄜州作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Huy-Tr%E1%BB%A9/Ca-di%C3%AAn-h%E1%BB%AFu-s%E1%BB%9F-ki%E1%BA%BFn/poem-cz0XnpNhcjD2Yfl2qnIhCg">Ca diên hữu sở kiến - 歌筵有所見</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Huy-Tr%E1%BB%A9/author-l-vfhV6KqRexQyEkpib8Ng">Đặng Huy Trứ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-C%C3%A2u/Ho%E1%BA%A1-L%C3%BD-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-x%C3%A1-%C4%90%C3%B4ng-nh%E1%BA%ADt-th%C6%B0-s%E1%BB%B1/poem-UXA5KZr7Oira1TlElNdMUg">Hoạ Lý thượng xá “Đông nhật thư sự” - 和李上舍冬日書事</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-C%C3%A2u/author-cKa6PCke-9dKEXrXIlCSzg">Hàn Câu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-V%C4%A9-Nghi%E1%BB%87p/L%C3%A2m-%C4%90%E1%BB%91n-nhi/poem-6dxU0HXnV8dJaXK0Gv5fYg">Lâm Đốn nhi - 臨頓兒</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-V%C4%A9-Nghi%E1%BB%87p/author-clxY5GFWegDsEw0Y8VPiNQ">Ngô Vĩ Nghiệp</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Mao-%C4%91%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-ki%E1%BB%83m-hi%E1%BB%87u-thu-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1o-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-1Qx5AmoG4ccNeGZcWFetDw">Mao đường kiểm hiệu thu đạo kỳ 2 - 茅堂檢校收稻其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%